        <FormAndLineReferenceDesc>Form 990, Part III, Line 4a-4c Description of program services</FormAndLineReferenceDesc>
        <ExplanationTxt>(Expenses $ 682,872 including grants of $)(Revenue $ 719,173) THE SENIOR NUTRITION PROGRAM OFFERS NUTRITIOUS MEALS AND VALUABLE NUTRITION EDUCATION TO ELIGIBLE SENIORS AGED 60 AND ABOVE IN BROWARD COUNTY. FUNDED BY THE AREA AGENCY ON AGING BROWARD COUNTY THROUGH THE OLDER AMERICANS ACT, THIS PROGRAM SUPPORTS VULNERABLE SENIORS BY PROVIDING A WELCOMING SPACE FOR THEM TO ENJOY HEALTHY MEALS AND PARTICIPATE IN GROUP NUTRITION EDUCATION SESSIONS. SERVING 500 SENIORS DAILY THROUGHOUT THE YEAR, THE PROGRAM PLAYS A CRUCIAL ROLE IN ENHANCING THE WELL-BEING OF OUR SENIOR COMMUNITY.</ExplanationTxt>
      </SupplementalInformationDetail>
